Émile Genevois https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89mile_Genevois 0 Émile Genevois (January 1, 1918 – September 19, 1962) was a French film actor. Genevois appeared in over ninety films and television programmes, generally in character roles. Émile_Genevois ( January_1_,_1918 – September_19_,_1962 ) was a_French_film_actor .
